Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

{
  "propertyId": "{{PROPERTY_ID}}"
}

### Favorites - List My Favorites
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/favorites/me
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

### Favorites - Remove
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/v1/favorites/{{PROPERTY_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

### Evaluations - Create (User/Owner/Admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/evaluations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

{
  "employeeId": "{{EMPLOYEE_ID}}",
  "appointmentId": "{{APPOINTMENT_ID}}",
  "rating": 5,
  "comments": "excellent experience"
}

### Evaluations - List (Admin/Employee)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/evaluations?employeeId={{EMPLOYEE_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{EMPLOYEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Email Logs - Create (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/email-logs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "userId": "{{CUSTOMER_ID}}",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "subject": "Test",
  "message": "Hello",
  "status": "Sent"
}

### Email Logs - List (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/email-logs?status=Sent
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Tasks To Employee - Assign (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/tasks-to-employees
