}

### Tasks By Employee - List (Admin/Employee)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/tasks-by-employees?employeeId={{EMPLOYEE_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{EMPLOYEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN}}


### Transactions - Create Transaction (Admin/Employee)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{EMPLOYEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "propertyId": "{{PROPERTY_ID}}",
  "customerId": "{{CUSTOMER_ID}}",
  "employeeId": "{{EMPLOYEE_ID}}",
  "transactionType": "بيع",
  "totalAmount": 2500000,
  "paidAmount": 500000
}

### Transactions - List Transactions (Admin/Employee)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/transactions?propertyId={{PROPERTY_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{EMPLOYEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Transactions - Get Transaction By Id (Admin/Employee)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/v1/transactions/{{TRANSACTION_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{EMPLOYEE_OR_ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Transactions - Update Transaction (Admin/Employee)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/v1/transactions/{{TRANSACTION_ID}}
